<subSubSection lastPageId="61" lastPageNumber="62" pageId="60" pageNumber="61" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="60.[151,1436,1839,2022]" pageId="60" pageNumber="61">
REMARKS: The earliest mention of 
<taxonomicName authority="Meigen, 1803" authorityName="Meigen" authorityYear="1803" box="[560,838,1957,1983]" class="Insecta" family="Chloropidae" genus="Chlorops" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="60" pageNumber="61" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[560,669,1957,1982]" italics="true" pageId="60" pageNumber="61">Chlorops</emphasis>
Meigen, 1803
</taxonomicName>
using the spelling “ 
<emphasis box="[1070,1153,1957,1982]" italics="true" pageId="60" pageNumber="61">Clorop</emphasis>
s” that we have found in this study is in 
<bibRefCitation author="Guerin-Meneville, F. E." box="[424,715,1996,2022]" pageId="60" pageNumber="61" pagination="xxii - xxiii" refId="ref131439" refString="Guerin-Meneville, F. E. (1845) [Report.] Annales de la Societe Entomologique de France, (2) 3, xxii - xxiii. [August] [Dated from C. D. Sherborn manuscript notes.]" type="journal article" year="1845">Guérin-Méneville (1845</bibRefCitation>
: xxii), as an incorrect subsequent spelling. In 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[1251,1435,1996,2022]" pageId="60" pageNumber="61" pagination="10" refId="ref144790" refString="Rondani, C. (1856) Dipterologiae italicae prodromus. Vol: I. Genera italica ordinis dipterorum ordinatim disposita et distincta et in familias et stirpes aggregata. A. Stocchi, Parmae [= Parma]. 226 + [2] pp. [10 September] [Dated from advertisement from publisher in Stettiner Entomologische Zeitung.]" type="journal article" year="1856">Rondani (1856)</bibRefCitation>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="61.[247,1436,158,262]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">
this is either an incorrect subsequent spelling or unjustified emendation (by virtue of similar spelling changes in two or more names from “ch” to “c” in the same work). We thus follow ICZN 
<emphasis box="[1374,1436,198,223]" italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">Code</emphasis>
Article 33.5 in treating this spelling in 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[701,885,236,262]" pageId="61" pageNumber="62" pagination="10" refId="ref144790" refString="Rondani, C. (1856) Dipterologiae italicae prodromus. Vol: I. Genera italica ordinis dipterorum ordinatim disposita et distincta et in familias et stirpes aggregata. A. Stocchi, Parmae [= Parma]. 226 + [2] pp. [10 September] [Dated from advertisement from publisher in Stettiner Entomologische Zeitung.]" type="journal article" year="1856">Rondani (1856)</bibRefCitation>
as an incorrect subsequent spelling.
</paragraph>
